BIKE STORE
We have a database with nine tables containing information about a bicycle store´s products, sales, customers, stock, staff, stores, and orders.  The task is to write a query in SQL in order to present the following information in Tableau for the year 2018:
•	Yearly Revenue (comparison for the 3 years 2016, 2017 and 2018).
•	Sales by Store
•	Sales by State
•	Sales by: Product, category, and brand
•	Quantities sold
•	Unique number of orders
•	Unique Number of customers
•	Number of repeating customers
•	Top sales reps
•	Top customers
